We provide this program in the hope that it may be useful to others, and we would very much like to hear about your experience with it. If you found it helpful and are using it within your software, we encourage you to get in touch with us.

Since a lot of time and effort has gone into Bazinga's development, please cite the following publication if you are using Bazinga for your own research:

* A. De Marchi, **[Augmented Lagrangian Proximal methods for constrained structured optimization](...)**, ... ([preprint](...))
  
  
